	<p>
	  The following is a line by line description of the Snippet HTML code.
	</p>

      <div class="code-view">
        <table class="code-table">
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td class="code-view-code-cell">&lt;script src="https://snippets.chc.ucsb.edu/ewxmapG5.js"&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
